    Method and Description
    dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJIInspireCamera.downloadAllSelectedFiles(String, DJIFileDownloadCallBack)
    This function will be replaced by downloadAllSelectedFiles(File, DJIFileDownloadCallBack).
    dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJICamera.downloadAllSelectedFiles(String, DJIFileDownloadCallBack)
    This function will be replaced by downloadAllSelectedFiles(File, DJIFileDownloadCallBack).
    dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJIInspireCamera.fetchMediaData(DJIMedia, DJIReceivedFileDataCallBack)
    Please use fetchMediaThumbnail(final File destDir, final DJIMediaInfo mDjiMedia, final DJIDownloadListener mCall)
    dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJIInspireCamera.fetchMediaList(DJIMediaFetchCallBack)
    Please use fetchMediaList(final DJIDownloadListener mCall)
    dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJIInspireCamera.fetchMediaThumbnail(DJIMedia, DJIExecuteResultCallback)
    Please use fetchMediaThumbnail(final File destDir, final DJIMediaInfo mDjiMedia, final DJIDownloadListener mCall)
